:"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"vim-lsp が補完とかの時に出すドキュメントのポップアップウィンドウで、 `**foo**` みたいな装飾文字の背景色がポップアップの背景色ではなくて通常バッファの背景色になってしまうのって、直すの難しいのですっけ","ts":"1606651785.096900","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"OABH"}]},{"client_msg_id":"de9ee6b7-a1f4-445c-bd7e-5cb99c48dbf7","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"まあ、そうなると vim-efm-langserver-settings も柔軟性が上るけど、よほどでなれば設定ファイルバンドルですんでるしな...","ts":"1606622575.095000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"tpPfN"}]},{"client_msg_id":"0569f189-a54b-4695-b19d-a6606703fcfc","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"この方、config.yaml なしがゴールなんですよね。","ts":"1606621897.094200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"YxKc"}]}]
